                            <comment id="12906116" author="daijy" created="Fri, 3 Sep 2010 22:35:53 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good. This patch is to address the problem that we cannot get output schema of the scalar UDF at compile time. Another approach is write ReadScalars.outputSchema(), and use the input schema to figure out the output schema. But again we need to address the dependency to make sure input schema is correctly set before calling outputSchema(). So both approach should be equivalent.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
